  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients with histology proven non-small cell lung cancer or a lesion suspicious of
             non-small cell lung cancer (lung cancer group)

          -  Healthy donors (control group)

          -  written informed consent

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Autoimmune disease

          -  Patients receiving immunomodulatory drugs, e.g. tacrolimus

          -  Prior malignancy

          -  Pregnancy
      </textblock>
